{{Vgname|模擬市民4：露天度假|en=The Sims 4: Outdoor Retreat}}是[[電腦遊戲|電腦遊戲]]《[[模擬市民4|模擬市民4]]》的第一款游戏包，于2015年1月13日发布。包括新的目的地、新物件、新着装以及新互动。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cinemablend.com/games/Sims-4-Outdoor-Retreat-Game-Pack-Announced-69058.html |title=The Sims 4 Outdoor Retreat Game Pack Announced |access-date=2015-04-02 |archive-date=2015-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923224329/http://www.cinemablend.com/games/Sims-4-Outdoor-Retreat-Game-Pack-Announced-69058.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

该游戏包繼承了[[模擬市民|模擬市民]]三代資料片《[[模擬市民3：世界歷險記|世界歷險記]]》、二代資料片《[[模擬市民2：環遊世界|環遊世界]]》及一代資料片《[[模擬市民：歡樂假期|歡樂假期]]》的遊戲特色，模擬-{}-市民能夠卸下平日沉重的工作和學業，探索一個各有特色的旅遊景點。<ref>[http://geeksdontlie.co.uk/sims-4-gets-new-add-content-outdoor-retreat-game-pack/ The Sims 4 gets new add-on content with the Outdoor Retreat game pack] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402115507/http://geeksdontlie.co.uk/sims-4-gets-new-add-content-outdoor-retreat-game-pack/ |date=2015-04-02 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2015/01/13/sims-4-expansion-outdoor-retreat-released-today/128813/ Sims 4 Game Pack ‘Outdoor Retreat’ Available Today] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2015/01/13/sims-4-expansion-outdoor-retreat-released-today/128813/ |date=20160304022932 }}2015-01-13</ref>

